    public interface HasAllSummernoteHandlers
extends HasSummernoteInitHandlers, HasSummernoteEnterHandlers, HasSummernoteFocusHandlers, HasSummernoteBlurHandlers, HasSummernoteKeyUpHandlers, HasSummernoteKeyDownHandlers, HasSummernotePasteHandlers, HasSummernoteImageUploadHandlers, HasSummernoteChangeHandlers
